ActNational Capital Act
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to renew a ground lease held by THE ROMAN CATHOLIC EPISCOPAL CORPORATION OF OTTAWA with respect to some 0.58 hectares of land situate at 2080 Merivale Road in Ottawa, being the site of St. Monica's Catholic Church, for a further term of 25 years.
